Make sure nodejs is installed and npm is installed.
Windows:
Download the LTS installer from the below website.
https://nodejs.org/en/#download

Linux/Mac:
Follow the installation guide from the below website and choose your own operating system.
https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/#windows

Then clone the project from Gitlab

Using the terminal 
1. cd to the Web_Development folder 
2. type "npm install"